<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Add_Host</title>

    <style>
      body{
        background-color: #e1dbdb;
      }
      .card {
  background-color: #caeb65;
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  margin: 20px auto;
  max-width: 600px;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
}

.card-header {
  background-color: #333;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 20px;
}

.card-body {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  padding: 20px;
}

.subdiv {
  background-color: #f2f2f2;
  border-radius: 5px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  flex: 1;
  margin: 10px;
  padding: 20px;
  position: relative;
}

.left:before {
  background-color: #333;
  content: '';
  height: 100%;
  left: -50%;
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  transform: skewX(-15deg);
  width: 50%;
}

.right:before {
  background-color: #333;
  content: '';
  height: 100%;
  position: absolute;
  right: -50%;
  top: 0;
  transform: skewX(-15deg);
  width: 50%;
}

.subdiv p {
  color: #333;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

label {
  display: block;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

input[type="file"] {
  border: none;
  display: block;
  font-size: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  padding: 10px;
  width: 100%;
}

button[type="submit"] {
  background-color: #333;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
  color: #fff;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 18px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
}

button[type="submit"]:hover {
  background-color: #fff;
  color: #333;
  transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.subdiv:hover {
  background-color: #ddd;
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
  
    
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <h2>Airbnb Host Upload</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="subdiv left">
        <p>Dear <b><u><%=userName.name %></u></b> for giving a Service of host in Airbnb First upload your hotel Image.</p>
        <p>After confirmation we will contact you!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="subdiv right">
        <form action="/AddHost" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
          <label for="image">Upload Image:</label>
          <input type="file" name="image" id="image">
          <button type="submit">Upload</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>